   1: 46.68935      1  3.8755119 treatment
   2: 53.52666      1  3.2816799 treatment
   3: 47.86065      1  0.8515517 treatment
   4: 47.94281      1 10.1313180 treatment
   5: 45.53314      1  2.6198951 treatment
